data.description: What an exceptional, beautiful place to call home!  If you're looking for a home that has everything you need for comfortable living, then look no further than this perfect property located in Cascata Lakes! With large open spaces, on almost 1/3 acre, it's perfect for those who love to entertain or just need room to stretch out and relax. Absolutely nothing for you to do but move in.  The beautiful real hardwood floors are both stylish and practical, adding a touch of elegance, while the newly installed carpet (designer carpet in bonus room & stairway) adds the perfect finishing touch.  The real showstopper of this property is the resort-style backyard!  With a sparkling pool (serviced weekly & comes with a custom-made, removable safety fence), lovely landscaping, and plenty of space for lounging, it's like having your own private oasis right in your own backyard. Imagine spending your weekends relaxing by the pool with a good book or hosting a BBQ for all your friends and family. The possibilities are endless!  Property includes:  4 large bedrooms, 2 living areas, new double-hung windows throughout, beautiful hardwood floors, new carpet in bedrooms, new designer carpet in bonus room & stairway, lovely formal dining, large kitchen w/breakfast bar, island & pantry, plantation shutters in office, updated interior paint 3-car garage, granite counters, 8-person storm shelter, built 2014, New roof Dec 2022, new hot water heaters, gunite pool with waterfall & tanning ledge,  new pool pumps & vacuum, extra-large  covered patio, & storage building.   So if you're looking for a home that has it all, this property is definitely worth considering. With its open spaces and large backyard with privacy fence (completely lined with exterior party lights) you won't be disappointed.  All in all, this home is a true gem and the perfect place to put down roots and create lasting memories with loved ones.  Owner is currently tax exempt.
